title: january 22: a building for an empire (state)
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the construction of the Empire State Building, for which excavation began today in 1930. Then, Maia talks about a musical comeback. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
